Package com.google.genkit.core.tracing

Class GenkitSpanData

java.lang.Object
com.google.genkit.core.tracing.GenkitSpanData
public class GenkitSpanData extends Object
GenkitSpanData represents information about a trace span. This format matches the telemetry server API expectations.
